The guy is an amazing fighter, and I have a lot of respect for that, but man he comes of as one hell of a douche too (and I'm not talking about his MAGA act). Still, the stoppage might've been a bit early. A rematch still shouldn't be in the cards since it is clear that Usman would've also won on the scorecards (and rightfully so). Either Masvidal or Edwards should get their shot first.
